Package src.repository

Class MedicalRecordRepository

java.lang.Object
src.repository.MedicalRecordRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMedicalRecordBasicOperations, IMedicalRecordDoctorOperations, IMedicalRecordMedicineOperations, IMedicalRecordRepository
public class MedicalRecordRepository extends Object implements IMedicalRecordRepository
Repository class for managing medical records in the system. Implements the IMedicalRecordRepository interface to provide CRUD operations and other medical record-related functionalities.
